original_title: Arnold Schoenberg, op. 11 - I - Cute Kittens
overview: Drei Klavierstuke is a recreation of Arnold Schoenberg’s 1909 op. 11 Drei Klavierstücke (aka Three Piano Pieces) made by editing together videos of cats playing pianos downloaded from Youtube.
title: Arnold Schoenberg, op. 11 - I - Cute Kittens
